author: Tom O'Connor
title: Israel's Benjamin Netanyahu, Close Aides Placed in Coronavirus COVID-19 Quarantine
description: Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu's office said the leader and several close aides would be placed in temporary quarantine after his adviser on parliamentary affairs tested positive for COVID-19.
content:
Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu has reportedly been placed under precautionary quarantine amid fears they could be exposed to the new coronavirus disease known as COVID-19.
